{
  "texts": [
    "We perform pretraining with flash attention 2 (Dao, 2023).",
    "We employ a sequence length of up to 8k tokens, thus accommodating long financial documents.",
    "We use LoRA (Hu et al., 2021) for pretraining and train the model for one epoch with a learning rate of 2.5e -5.",
    "Pretraining takes 80 hours on four 40GB A100 GPUs.",
    "Prompting for Financial LLMs We employ a prompting method suited for a financial LLM with multimodal capabilities."
  ]
}